Package jaengine.modules.physics

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • jaengine.logic.Node<GameObject>
      • jaengine.modules.physics.GameObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Block, Environment
    public class GameObject
extends Node<GameObject>
    The GameObject class represents GameoBjects that can be in an envionment. It inherits from Node, so it benefits from being both a node and being itself.
